msgid ""
"All taught lessons (status 'taught') in the specified period will be "
"automatically included in the invoice. Lessons with status 'planned' or "
"'paid' will not be considered. A lesson can only appear in one invoice - "
"lessons that are already included in another invoice will be automatically "
"excluded."
